{"lemma":"خاسِرِي","slug":"خاسِرِي","root":"خ.س.ر","root_slug":"خ-س-ر","root_link":"/words/roots/خ-س-ر","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"خاسِر","root":"خسر","pos":"N","occurrence_count":32},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["adj"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":1},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n10601"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AE%D8%A7%D8%B3%D9%90%D8%B1%D9%90%D9%8A"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"adj","gloss":"active participle of خَسِرَ (ḵasira)","tags":["active","form-of","participle"]}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Derived from the active participle of the verb خَسِرَ (ḵasira, “to lose”)."},"ipa":["/xaː.sir/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n10601","headword_ar":"خَاسِرٌ","root":"xsr","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Losing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"suffering loss, in his traffic."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lth.) And [hence,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tijaArapN xaAsirapN","text_ar":"تِجَارَةٌ خَاسِرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Losing traffic; traffic which is an occasion of loss"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; opposed to"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raAbiHapN","text_ar":"رَابِحَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (A.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SafoqapN xaAsirapN","text_ar":"صَفْقَةٌ خَاسِرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A bargain that does not bring gain"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"but"},{"kind":"text","text":"on the contrary"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"occasions loss"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kar~apN xaAsirapN","text_ar":"كَرَّةٌ خَاسِرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"An unprofitable charge"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"assault."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) ―         -b2-  One"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"who has lost his property,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"his intellect."},{"kind":"text","text":"(IAar.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Erring; going astray; deviating from,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"losing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"missing, the right way:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"becoming lost; perishing;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"dying:"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DaAl~N","text_ar":"ضَالٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K:) and so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xasirN","text_ar":"خَسِرٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xasiyrN","text_ar":"خَسِيرٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xayosaraY","text_ar":"خَيْسَرَى","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K, TA, but the last written in the CK"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xayosariY~N","text_ar":"خَيْسَرِىٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":",) or ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xayosarN","text_ar":"خَيْسَرٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", for it is said to occur [as an epithet] only in the following saying, in which"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xayosaraY","text_ar":"خَيْسَرَى"},{"kind":"text","text":"is said to be put for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xayosarN","text_ar":"خَيْسَرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"to assimilate it to preceding words:"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bifiyhi","text_ar":"بِفِيهِ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlbaraY wa Hum~aY xayobaraY wa $ar~N maA yaraY faA_in~ahu xayosaraY","text_ar":"البَرَى وَ حُمَّى خَيْبَرَى وَ شَرٌّ مَا يَرَى فَاـِنَّهُ خَيْسَرَى"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"In his mouth be dust, and"},{"kind":"text","text":"may"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the fever of Kheyber"},{"kind":"text","text":"befall him,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and evil be that which he shall see, for he is one who goeth astray:"},{"kind":"text","text":"but in the TA, in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wrY","text_ar":"ورى"},{"kind":"text","text":", is another reading; for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bfyh AlbrY","text_ar":"بفيه البرى"},{"kind":"text","text":", substituting"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bihi AlwaraY","text_ar":"بِهِ الوَرَى"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning a certain disease]. (TA.) [Hence,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aHomaqu xaAsirN daAbirN daAmirN","text_ar":"اَحْمَقُ خَاسِرٌ دَابِرٌ دَامِرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Foolish,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"stupid, erring, and utterly perishing"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (T in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bt","text_ar":"بت"},{"kind":"text","text":". [See"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baAt~N","text_ar":"بَاتٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":": and see also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"daAmirN","text_ar":"دَامِرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".]) ―         -b4-  Also One"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"who makes the measure,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the balance, defective,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"deficient, when he gives, and demands excess when he receives."},{"kind":"text","text":"(AA.)"}],"source_refs":["K","TA"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}